Package org.skistation.models.DTO

Class BuyTicketRequest

java.lang.Object
org.skistation.models.DTO.BuyTicketRequest
public class BuyTicketRequest extends Object
Represents a request to buy a ticket. It contains the client, ticket details, total price, number of normal and discount tickets, and the price list.

      public BuyTicketRequest(Client client, TicketDTO ticketDTO, Float total, Integer numberOfNormalPasses, Integer numberOfDiscountPasses, PriceList priceList)
      Constructs a new BuyTicketRequest with the specified client, ticket details, total price, number of normal and discount tickets, and price list.
      Parameters:
      client - the client who wants to buy the ticket
      ticketDTO - the details of the ticket to buy
      total - the total price of the ticket
      numberOfNormalPasses - the number of normal tickets to buy
      numberOfDiscountPasses - the number of discount tickets to buy
      priceList - the price list for the ticket
